# Report

## EXISTING STRUCTURES

## ERROR TIPS

### Errors when using extracting but being too far
 -  Make sure to move to the target entity where you want to extract from before extracting items

### Errors when placing into a tile which is occupied by another entity
- Ensure you can place a entity to a tile before attempting placing

### Errors when extracting
- Ensure that the target entity has items to extract before attempting to extract items.

### Errors when inserting
- Ensure that the target entity has space for items to insert before attempting to insert items.

### Errors when getting an entity
- Ensure that the entity exists at the position before attempting to get it.

### Errors when clearing furnace inventories
- Ensure that the furnace has items to extract before attempting to extract items.

### Errors when inserting iron ore into furnace
- Ensure that the furnace has space for iron ore before attempting to insert iron ore.

### Errors when getting transport belt
- Ensure that the transport belt exists at the position before attempting to get it. Double check that the transport belt exists at the specified position.

## NAMESPACE
